# PATCH 002: Copilot Claude endpoint routing, thinking support, and copilot- prefix handling
#
# Routes Claude models (opus-4, sonnet-4, etc.) to /v1/messages endpoint
# with Claude-native format. Enables thinking/reasoning with sensible defaults.
# Routes GPT-5 models to /responses endpoint via codex format. Strips copilot- prefix
# from model names in registry lookups, provider resolution, and upstream requests.
# Adds SSE passthrough for Claude streaming, usage fallback, and
# convertPlainClaudeResponseToOpenAI for non-streaming responses.
# Stabilizes rotating encrypted IDs in Responses API events.

